In the subdivisions listed in this subsection, the hours during which alcoholic beverages may be sold or delivered to retail license holders by holders of manufacturers' licenses are from 6 a.m. to midnight, on every day except Sundays:
Allegany County;
Anne Arundel County;
Baltimore County;
Calvert County;
Carroll County;
Cecil County;
Charles County;
Frederick County;
Harford County;
Howard County;
Kent County;
Prince George's County;
Queen Anne's County;
Somerset County;
Wicomico County; and
Worcester County.
